# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .easignore — Files excluded from EAS Build upload
#
# EAS uploads everything tracked by git. This file excludes content that is
# not needed to build the mobile app, keeping the upload small and fast.
#
# Rule of thumb: if it's not mobile app source or mobile assets, exclude it.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Research / IP data (largest offender: ~800 MB) ───────────────────────────
Local data/

# ── Backend & engine (server-side code, not needed for mobile build) ──────────
nick_brain/

# ── Documentation & brand assets ─────────────────────────────────────────────
docs/

# ── Infrastructure (Terraform, Docker, etc.) ─────────────────────────────────
infra/

# ── Build artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/dist/
**/build/
**/*-dist/
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# ── Environment files (secrets must never be uploaded) ───────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ── Development tooling ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.cursor/
.claude/
.vscode/
.idea/

# ── OS artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Logs ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
